__data__.text: Name: Jon Legasa Email: jon.legasa@gmail.com Phone: (646) 965-2264 GitHub: https://github.com/jonxlegasa LinkedIn: https://www.linkedin.com/in/jon-legasa-615986253/  Professional Summary Computer Science major at Baruch College, skilled in web technologies, database management, and AI Engineering.
